name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Federal Court of Canada E-Filing Assistant

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: File faster at the Federal Court of Canada

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Auto-fill standard filing information in the Federal Court and Federal Court of Appeal of Canada's electronic filing system so that you do not need to re-enter it every time.

Created by a Canadian lawyer who regularly practices at the Federal Courts to streamline filing and eliminate repetitive tasks.

(Not affiliated with the Federal Courts of Canada)
